quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,Olabye oyo alimbisa olunaku lw'enkomerero
  107,2,Oyo nno y’oyo awalagganya ba mulekwa
  107,3,Era nga takubiriza kuliisa banaku
  107,4,Okubonaabona kuli ku abo abasaala
  107,5,Nga balagajjalira e sswala zaabwe
  107,6,Abo abakola bandabe
  107,7,Era abamma bannaabwe ebintu ebitasaana kumma